      "writtenOn": "2019-07-16T17:34:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "kBufferSize is only used in one place, and it’s needlessly separated from this declaration.\n\nInstead, just write:\n\n  wchar_t buffer[1024];\n\nAlso, better to name after what it’s storing, so:\n\n  wchar_t vendor_identifier[1024];",
